{"tid":640457,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[有片]傳真社獲cctv片：4月2日橫水渡起火疑有易燃液體　在場人仕指 警方曾稱閉路電視冇拍下事發當日畫面","createTime":"2018-04-24T09:44:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-25T02:52:55.000Z","uid":48083,"like":7,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"3f4d7ef5816258336c61532538193862ac16d265","tid":640457,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T09:44:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180424/s00001/a24f286ac7ac2b61270426095e14184d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180424%2Fs00001%2Fa24f286ac7ac2b61270426095e14184d.jpg&h=6ef81f81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n片:<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180424/s00001/1524555551982\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180424%2Fs00001%2F1524555551982&d=zVjBJXvXBebaGoQd0jZlrYS5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=3ac440a4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180424%2Fs00001%2F1524555551982&h=55119738\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180424/s00001/1524555551982</a><br />\n<br />\n元朗南生圍近日接連發生縱火事件，燒毀的包括著名景點橫水渡碼頭木船，惟至今仍未破案。傳真社取得橫水渡起火當日閉路電視片段，發現起火時疑似有易燃液體流出，在水面流動並着火，而最少兩人目擊火警，卻沒有報警。<br />\n<br />\n橫水渡碼頭縱火案發生在本月2日。傳真社取得安裝於橫水渡收費處上的閉路電視片段，顯示渡頭當日凌晨2時55分起火，其間有疑似易燃液體流出，並在水面上燃燒。<br />\n<br />\n火勢持續約個半小時後（凌晨4點30分），有一人在對岸渡頭小路走出渡頭，望向着火位置約1分鐘，然後轉身離開。至天亮前、約5時24分，再有一名男子在對岸出現，走到渡頭觀察火勢，其間疑似使用電話，約3分鐘後離開。最終橫水渡負責人譚根於6時許報警，消防員到場救火，木船則只燒剩船底及船頭。<br />\n<br />\n傳真社引述港大化學系退休教授馮應昇表示，難以憑肉眼確定有關液體是什麼，但指「物質要比水輕才可以在水上漂浮，可以在水面燃燒的一定是易燃物體，火水、石油、汽油都具備這些條件」。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>傳真社又引述《明報》等多家傳媒消息，<span style=\"font-size: large;\">警方曾在渡頭取走閉路電視片段，但因拍攝裝置硬碟空間不足，未有錄下3月11日之後片段，</span>而譚根及橫水渡船隻持牌人林先生都表示，警方曾向他們稱，閉路電視未有拍下事發當日畫面。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n警方回覆傳真社指，元朗警區重案組第三隊正積極調查有關縱火案，並已取走閉路電視片段跟進，暫時無人被捕，但無回應是否曾說閉路電視未有錄下事發片段。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180424/s00001/1524555551982\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180424%2Fs00001%2F1524555551982&d=zVjBJXvXBebaGoQd0jZlrYS5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=3ac440a4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180424%2Fs00001%2F1524555551982&h=55119738\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180424/s00001/1524555551982</a>"},{"pid":"5664a182192d7588f9cfd6c8046c0e596b00f19e","tid":640457,"uid":61462,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T10:06:47.000Z","msg":"警察<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4587d0195bf10ea622bc69c66643870697f6834e","tid":640457,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T10:13:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2b8a0bbbc7f9617bb079603d5f8f8671c66fe989","tid":640457,"uid":49316,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T10:15:53.000Z","msg":"唔係有超級電腦<br />\n<br />\n黒警<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff37158a6c40dd5bbcaf7f22e46909fe70594695","tid":640457,"uid":5026,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T10:16:07.000Z","msg":"羅生門"},{"pid":"7eb026eb40453883bd831109bcd251b8c631f9fc","tid":640457,"uid":6211,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T10:20:14.000Z","msg":"警方經費不足 影響調查"},{"pid":"d3fd17bb62b4ca756e61ab7